{"tid":1906326,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［武肺］員工擔心疫情拒絕上班 羅浮宮被迫全日閉館","createTime":"2020-03-02T00:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T09:53:29.000Z","uid":240250,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"84c8597ac5a530c1c79399eaa166f5a80e68570d","tid":1906326,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T00:16:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/441913\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F441913&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igSiczFR88nQiTnqliI8U3YY%3D&h=645159d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/441913</a><br />\n<br />\n準時返工喇香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd7d6381415ea9b191a47109a0e185ec98f0125","tid":1906326,"uid":188176,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T00:17:45.000Z","msg":"法國佬理鳩你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n番工？fuck?"},{"pid":"792b07c131a1894a591b036cb71843faed85f614","tid":1906326,"uid":240250,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T00:18:19.000Z","msg":"俗稱武漢肺炎的新型冠狀病毒疫情持續，法國巴黎羅浮宮（Louvre Museum）的員工周日（3月1日）因憂慮受感染而集體行使「不上班權」（droit de retrait），導致博物館當天全日關閉。<br />\n<br />\n羅浮宮每日均接待大量來自世界各地的旅客，因此員工認為受感染的風險很高，非常擔心，要求管理層加強保障。館方努力嘗試釋除員工疑慮，然而雙方的討論未如理想；工會代表稱，開館前召開了員工大會，共有300人出席，最終有298人投票贊成行使「不上班權」，僅2人投反對票。<br />\n<br />\n網上片段顯示，羅浮宮當日上午入口仍大排長龍，民眾等候入內參觀，惟羅浮宮直至下午也無法開放，館方約在下午5時始宣佈全日閉館。<br />\n<br />\n消息指出，員工有機會在未來數天再次行使「不上班權」，並呼籲目前身在巴黎且有意參觀羅浮宮的人士注意。根據當地的勞工法例，如果員工有合理理由懷疑工作環境會對其生命及安全構成嚴重威脅，有權通知公司負責人不上班。<br />\n<br />\n法國迄今確診受感染人數逾100人，其中2人死亡，12人出院，9人情況嚴重。當局上周六（29日）宣布暫時禁止超過5000人的公眾集會，但衛生部長韋朗（Olivier Veran）透露，當局稍後或會修改內容，希望能盡快控制疫情和解除禁令。受到禁令影響，原定在3月1日舉行、吸引4萬名跑手參加的巴黎半馬拉松賽事被迫取消，當地的年度農產展亦提早一日結束。<br />\n<br />\n另外，巴黎大主教要求教區神父不要將聖餐麵包直接放入信眾的嘴巴；當局又建議民眾打招呼時避免傳統的親吻臉頰方式。"},{"pid":"00cc5c2cc52d6f0f3bb52b7af87ce2cb59401f65","tid":1906326,"uid":276715,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T00:18:49.000Z","msg":"好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n值得各國奴隸學習"},{"pid":"43a441aaa75a261944a048993ed767d5db93b46f","tid":1906326,"uid":128271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T00:36:23.000Z","msg":"另外兩個做咩唔返去開館維持運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd93a332657dffc9bde0d0181ec2e4fe247ad26","tid":1906326,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T01:10:37.000Z","msg":"準時返工喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad58c6120c72d8d57a4af0f958aaec4e0aeeb7a","tid":1906326,"uid":78599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efd93a332657dffc9bde0d0181ec2e4fe247ad26","tid":1906326,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T01:10:37.000Z","msg":"準時返工喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T01:11:48.000Z","msg":"垃圾表示返緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28564d2c7349c969c48686c5596bce33729b36b3","tid":1906326,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T01:26:54.000Z","msg":"想知點解有兩人投反對票？"},{"pid":"6c3ef57f8eca464c13580ff5c20e4f4f585c7c03","tid":1906326,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cad58c6120c72d8d57a4af0f958aaec4e0aeeb7a","tid":1906326,"uid":78599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efd93a332657dffc9bde0d0181ec2e4fe247ad26","tid":1906326,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T01:10:37.000Z","msg":"準時返工喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T01:11:48.000Z","msg":"垃圾表示返緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T01:44:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"h